---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import headshotImg from '../assets/Jelena-Djurovic-headshot.png';
import { providerLicenseNumber } from '../utils/seo';
---

<section class="bg-white py-14 xl:py-20">
  <div class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-5 md:px-10 xl:px-24">
    <div class="flex flex-col xl:flex-row items-start gap-10 xl:gap-16">

      <!-- Left: image -->
      <div class="w-full xl:flex-none xl:w-[500px] h-[350px] sm:h-[450px] md:h-[550px] xl:h-[600px] rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
        <Image 
          src={headshotImg} 
          alt="Dr. Jelena Djurovic" 
          class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top" 
          format="webp"
          quality={75}
          widths={[400, 800]} 
          sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 400px" 
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Right: content -->
      <div class="flex flex-col flex-1">
        <p class="text-sm xl:text-base text-black leading-normal">Meet Your Provider</p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 xl:mt-10 text-2xl md:text-3xl xl:text-[40px] font-bold text-black xl:leading-snug">
          Dr. Jelena Djurovic, Psy.D.
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-xs md:text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#2f594f]">
          Illinois Licensed Clinical Psychologist | License #{providerLicenseNumber}
        </p>

        <!-- Blockquote with green left bar -->
        <div class="mt-6 xl:mt-8 flex gap-5 xl:gap-7 items-start">
          <div class="w-3 h-10 xl:h-[42px] bg-primary flex-none rounded-sm mt-0.5" />
          <p class="text-sm xl:text-base font-bold text-black leading-7">
            "I believe in this day and age therapy is not a luxury, nor is it exclusively intended for those suffering from a mental illness, but it is rather a necessity and can be a benefit to nearly anyone in any kind of situation."
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Description -->
        <p class="mt-3 xl:mt-4 text-sm xl:text-base text-black leading-7">
          Dr. Djurovic is a licensed clinical psychologist in the state of Illinois with more than 10 years of clinical practice, including psychotherapy and assessment of individuals with wide array of psychological issues and of diverse backgrounds.
        </p>

        <!-- Metrics row hidden -->

        <!-- About button -->
        <div class="mt-6 xl:mt-8">
          <a
            href="/about"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 xl:px-10 py-3 xl:py-4 border-[1.4px] border-primary rounded-5xl text-sm xl:text-base font-bold text-primary hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-colors"
          >
            Meet Dr. Djurovic
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
